<D>__{a mine!}
<A>__{a glow from gandalf's staff suddenly lights the chamber... the fellowship recoil in horror! many dwarf skeletons are strewn about, clearly the dead of some old battle...the rusting armor and shields are peppered with arrows and axes.}
